{"data":[{"name":"92:1","price":"1. Par la nuit quand elle voile tout !","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6059,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshā ","translations":["By the night","when","it covers","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1640],[3,1640,2775]]}},{"name":"92:2","price":"2. Par le jour quand il est dans tout son éclat !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6060,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā tajallā ","translations":["And the day","when","it shines in brightness","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","tajallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,2570],[3,2570,3855]]}},{"name":"92:3","price":"3. Par ce qui[609] a créé le mâle et la femelle !","arabic":"وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6061,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[609] Sur la valeur de ce pronom relatif, voir la note précédente, qui renvoyait aux versets 5, 6 et 7 de la sourate Ach-Chams. ","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā khalaqa al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["And He Who","created","the male","and the female","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","khalaqa","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1260],[3,1260,2170],[4,2170,4415]]}},{"name":"92:4","price":"4. Vos efforts sont, en vérité, (déployés) pour des desseins divers.","arabic":"إِنَّ سَعۡيَكُمۡ لَشَتَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6062,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"inna saʿyakum lashattā ","translations":["Indeed","your efforts","(are) surely diverse","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","saʿyakum","lashattā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2330],[3,2330,3655]]}},{"name":"92:5","price":"5. Celui qui donne (de ses biens) et qui craint (Allah),","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أَعۡطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6063,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man aʿṭā wa-ittaqā ","translations":["Then as for","(him) who","gives","and fears","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","aʿṭā","wa-ittaqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2150],[3,2150,3050],[4,3050,4725]]}},{"name":"92:6","price":"6. Qui croit en la meilleure des récompenses,","arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6064,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣaddaqa bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And believes","in the best","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣaddaqa","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2425]]}},{"name":"92:7","price":"7. Nous le mettrons sur la voie la plus facile.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6065,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'yus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] ease","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'yus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1790],[2,1790,3725]]}},{"name":"92:8","price":"8. Quant à celui qui fait preuve d’avarice, se passe (de la récompense d’Allah),","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6066,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man bakhila wa-is'taghnā ","translations":["But as for","(him) who","withholds","and considers himself free from need","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","bakhila","wa-is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,2630],[3,2630,3250],[4,3250,4555]]}},{"name":"92:9","price":"9. et refuse de croire en la meilleure des récompenses,","arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6067,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wakadhaba bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And denies","the best","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wakadhaba","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2455]]}},{"name":"92:10","price":"10. Nous le mettrons sur la voie la plus difficile.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡعُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6068,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'ʿus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] difficulty","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'ʿus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1760],[2,1760,3555]]}},{"name":"92:11","price":"11. Ses biens ne lui seront en rien utiles quand il sera livré (au Feu).","arabic":"وَمَا يُغۡنِي عَنۡهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6069,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yugh'nī ʿanhu māluhu idhā taraddā ","translations":["And not","will avail","him","his wealth","when","he falls","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yugh'nī","ʿanhu","māluhu","idhā","taraddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1540],[3,1540,2130],[4,2130,4670],[5,4670,5280],[6,5280,6595]]}},{"name":"92:12","price":"12. À Nous incombe de guider (les hommes).","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا لَلۡهُدَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6070,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿalaynā lalhudā ","translations":["Indeed","upon Us","(is) the guidance","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿalaynā","lalhudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,2250],[3,2250,3435]]}},{"name":"92:13","price":"13. À Nous appartiennent la vie dans l’autre monde et la vie en ce bas monde.","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلۡأٓخِرَةَ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6071,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna lanā lalākhirata wal-ūlā ","translations":["And indeed","for Us","(is) the Hereafter","and the first (life)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","lanā","lalākhirata","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1360],[2,1360,2110],[3,2110,3550],[4,3550,5025]]}},{"name":"92:14","price":"14. Je vous mets en garde contre un Feu dévorant,","arabic":"فَأَنذَرۡتُكُمۡ نَارٗا تَلَظَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6072,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-andhartukum nāran talaẓẓā ","translations":["So I warn you","(of) a Fire","blazing","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-andhartukum","nāran","talaẓẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2650],[2,2650,4010],[3,4010,5555]]}},{"name":"92:15","price":"15. où ne brûlera que le réprouvé,","arabic":"لَا يَصۡلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6073,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yaṣlāhā illā al-ashqā ","translations":["Not","will burn (in) it","except","the most wretched","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yaṣlāhā","illā","al-ashqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,3279],[3,3279,3899],[4,3899,5524]]}},{"name":"92:16","price":"16. qui a osé démentir et s’est détourné avec dédain.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6074,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["The one who","denied","and turned away","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,2000],[3,2000,3405]]}},{"name":"92:17","price":"17. Il ne sera épargné qu’à l’homme pieux,","arabic":"وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَتۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6075,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wasayujannabuhā al-atqā ","translations":["But will be removed from it","the righteous","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wasayujannabuhā","al-atqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3040],[2,3040,4585]]}},{"name":"92:18","price":"18. qui dépense de ses biens pour se purifier,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُؤۡتِي مَالَهُۥ يَتَزَكَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6076,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yu'tī mālahu yatazakkā ","translations":["The one who","gives","his wealth","(to) purify himself","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yu'tī","mālahu","yatazakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,1890],[3,1890,3000],[4,3000,4515]]}},{"name":"92:19","price":"19. et ne le fait point pour rendre à quelqu’un la dette d’un bienfait,","arabic":"وَمَا لِأَحَدٍ عِندَهُۥ مِن نِّعۡمَةٖ تُجۡزَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6077,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā li-aḥadin ʿindahu min niʿ'matin tuj'zā ","translations":["And not","for anyone","with him","any","favor","to be recompensed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","li-aḥadin","ʿindahu","min","niʿ'matin","tuj'zā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1650],[3,1650,3320],[4,3320,3620],[5,3620,6310],[6,6310,7405]]}},{"name":"92:20","price":"20. mais pour être agréable à son Seigneur,[610] l’Altissime.","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱبۡتِغَآءَ وَجۡهِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6078,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[610] Littéralement : pour le Visage d’Allah : Wajhillah. Voir aussi le verset 272 de la sourate Al-Baqarah.","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ib'tighāa wajhi rabbihi al-aʿlā ","translations":["Except","seeking","(the) Countenance","(of) his Lord","the Most High","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ib'tighāa","wajhi","rabbihi","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,3409],[3,3409,3969],[4,3969,4879],[5,4879,6054]]}},{"name":"92:21","price":"21. Et il sera, assurément, satisfait.","arabic":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يَرۡضَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6079,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr","meta":{"transliteration":"walasawfa yarḍā ","translations":["And soon, surely","he will be pleased","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["walasawfa","yarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2285]]}}],"chapter":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail","Chapter Al-Lail","Lail","Surah Lail","Chapter Lail","Al Lail","Surah Al Lail","Chapter Al Lail","Surah 92","Chapter 92","The Night","الليل"],"version":{"key":"french_montada","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"fr","version":"1.0.0","last_update":1539205200,"title":"French Translation - Noor International Center","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into French, by Dr. Nabil Radwan, published by Noor International Center - was printed in 2017."}}